{"surahDetails":{"id":88,"arabicName":"الغاشية","banglaName":"বিহ্বলকর ঘটনা","englishName":"The Overwhelming","enTranslatedName":"Al-Ghashiyah","arLocation":"مكية","enLocation":"meccan","totalWords":92,"totalLetters":378,"audio":"http://download.quranicaudio.com/quran/ahmed_ibn_3ali_al-3ajamy/088.mp3","totalAyah":26},"surah":{"id":88,"verses":[{"id":1,"arabic_text":"هَلۡ أَتَىٰكَ حَدِيثُ ٱلۡغَٰشِيَةِ","bangl_text":"আপনার কাছে আচ্ছন্নকারী কেয়ামতের বৃত্তান্ত পৌঁছেছে কি","english_text":"Has there reached you the report of the Overwhelming [event]","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088001.mp3"},{"id":2,"arabic_text":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٍ خَٰشِعَةٌ","bangl_text":"অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে লাঞ্ছিত","english_text":"[Some] faces, that Day, will be humbled","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088002.mp3"},{"id":3,"arabic_text":"عَامِلَةٞ نَّاصِبَةٞ","bangl_text":"ক্লিষ্ট, ক্লান্ত।","english_text":"Working [hard] and exhausted","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088003.mp3"},{"id":4,"arabic_text":"تَصۡلَىٰ نَارًا حَامِيَةٗ","bangl_text":"তারা জ্বলন্ত আগুনে পতিত হবে।","english_text":"They will [enter to] burn in an intensely hot Fire","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088004.mp3"},{"id":5,"arabic_text":"تُسۡقَىٰ مِنۡ عَيۡنٍ ءَانِيَةٖ","bangl_text":"তাদেরকে ফুটন্ত নহর থেকে পান করানো হবে।","english_text":"They will be given drink from a boiling spring","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088005.mp3"},{"id":6,"arabic_text":"لَّيۡسَ لَهُمۡ طَعَامٌ إِلَّا مِن ضَرِيعٖ","bangl_text":"কন্টকপূর্ণ ঝাড় ব্যতীত তাদের জন্যে কোন খাদ্য নেই।","english_text":"For them there will be no food except from a poisonous, thorny plant","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088006.mp3"},{"id":7,"arabic_text":"لَّا يُسۡمِنُ وَلَا يُغۡنِي مِن جُوعٖ","bangl_text":"এটা তাদেরকে পুষ্ট করবে না এবং ক্ষুধায়ও উপকার করবে না।","english_text":"Which neither nourishes nor avails against hunger","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088007.mp3"},{"id":8,"arabic_text":"وُجُوهٞ يَوۡمَئِذٖ نَّاعِمَةٞ","bangl_text":"অনেক মুখমন্ডল সেদিন হবে, সজীব","english_text":"[Other] faces, that Day, will show pleasure","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088008.mp3"},{"id":9,"arabic_text":"لِّسَعۡيِهَا رَاضِيَةٞ","bangl_text":"তাদের কর্মের কারণে সন্তুষ্ট।","english_text":"With their effort [they are] satisfied","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088009.mp3"},{"id":10,"arabic_text":"فِي جَنَّةٍ عَالِيَةٖ","bangl_text":"তারা থাকবে, সুউচ্চ জান্নাতে।","english_text":"In an elevated garden","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088010.mp3"},{"id":11,"arabic_text":"لَّا تَسۡمَعُ فِيهَا لَٰغِيَةٗ","bangl_text":"তথায় শুনবে না কোন অসার কথাবার্তা।","english_text":"Wherein they will hear no unsuitable speech","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088011.mp3"},{"id":12,"arabic_text":"فِيهَا عَيۡنٞ جَارِيَةٞ","bangl_text":"তথায় থাকবে প্রবাহিত ঝরণা।","english_text":"Within it is a flowing spring","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088012.mp3"},{"id":13,"arabic_text":"فِيهَا سُرُرٞ مَّرۡفُوعَةٞ","bangl_text":"তথায় থাকবে উন্নত সুসজ্জিত আসন।","english_text":"Within it are couches raised high","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088013.mp3"},{"id":14,"arabic_text":"وَأَكۡوَابٞ مَّوۡضُوعَةٞ","bangl_text":"এবং সংরক্ষিত পানপাত্র","english_text":"And cups put in place","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088014.mp3"},{"id":15,"arabic_text":"وَنَمَارِقُ مَصۡفُوفَةٞ","bangl_text":"এবং সারি সারি গালিচা","english_text":"And cushions lined up","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088015.mp3"},{"id":16,"arabic_text":"وَزَرَابِيُّ مَبۡثُوثَةٌ","bangl_text":"এবং বিস্তৃত বিছানো কার্পেট।","english_text":"And carpets spread around","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088016.mp3"},{"id":17,"arabic_text":"أَفَلَا يَنظُرُونَ إِلَى ٱلۡإِبِلِ كَيۡفَ خُلِقَتۡ","bangl_text":"তারা কি উষ্ট্রের প্রতি লক্ষ্য করে না যে, তা কিভাবে সৃষ্টি করা হয়েছে","english_text":"Then do they not look at the camels - how they are created","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088017.mp3"},{"id":18,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَى ٱلسَّمَآءِ كَيۡفَ رُفِعَتۡ","bangl_text":"এবং আকাশের প্রতি লক্ষ্য করে না যে, তা কিভাবে উচ্চ করা হয়েছে","english_text":"And at the sky - how it is raised","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088018.mp3"},{"id":19,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡجِبَالِ كَيۡفَ نُصِبَتۡ","bangl_text":"এবং পাহাড়ের দিকে যে, তা কিভাবে স্থাপন করা হয়েছে","english_text":"And at the mountains - how they are erected","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088019.mp3"},{"id":20,"arabic_text":"وَإِلَى ٱلۡأَرۡضِ كَيۡفَ سُطِحَتۡ","bangl_text":"এবং পৃথিবীর দিকে যে, তা কিভাবে সমতল বিছানো হয়েছে","english_text":"And at the earth - how it is spread out","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088020.mp3"},{"id":21,"arabic_text":"فَذَكِّرۡ إِنَّمَآ أَنتَ مُذَكِّرٞ","bangl_text":"অতএব, আপনি উপদেশ দিন, আপনি তো কেবল একজন উপদেশদাতা","english_text":"So remind, [O Muhammad]; you are only a reminder","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088021.mp3"},{"id":22,"arabic_text":"لَّسۡتَ عَلَيۡهِم بِمُصَيۡطِرٍ","bangl_text":"আপনি তাদের শাসক নন","english_text":"You are not over them a controller","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088022.mp3"},{"id":23,"arabic_text":"إِلَّا مَن تَوَلَّىٰ وَكَفَرَ","bangl_text":"কিন্তু যে মুখ ফিরিয়ে নেয় ও কাফের হয়ে যায়","english_text":"However, he who turns away and disbelieves","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088023.mp3"},{"id":24,"arabic_text":"فَيُعَذِّبُهُ ٱللَّهُ ٱلۡعَذَابَ ٱلۡأَكۡبَرَ","bangl_text":"আল্লাহ তাকে মহা আযাব দেবেন।","english_text":"Then Allah will punish him with the greatest punishment","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088024.mp3"},{"id":25,"arabic_text":"إِنَّ إِلَيۡنَآ إِيَابَهُمۡ","bangl_text":"নিশ্চয় তাদের প্রত্যাবর্তন আমারই নিকট","english_text":"Indeed, to Us is their return","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088025.mp3"},{"id":26,"arabic_text":"ثُمَّ إِنَّ عَلَيۡنَا حِسَابَهُم","bangl_text":"অতঃপর তাদের হিসাব-নিকাশ আমারই দায়িত্ব।","english_text":"Then indeed, upon Us is their account","page":592,"is_sajdah_ayat":false,"audio":"https://everyayah.com/data/ahmed_ibn_ali_al_ajamy_128kbps/088026.mp3"}]}}